  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/04/evernote-for-mac-now-lets-you-search-using-everyday-language/\"><img alt=\"Natural language search on Evernote for Mac\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/97335fbfbf489dec1105c3ad3dc04911/evernote-mac-natural-language-search.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\nEvernote 要同步许多东西，但也正因为此，搜索起来总是需要一些技巧。不过在最近的 Mac 版更新中，开发团队让一切变得更简单了。用户在升级后将可以通过简单的日常用语来搜索内容，举例来说，你可以输入「上个月通过手机应用创建的附带有音频文件的笔记」，之后相关的文档便会出现在你眼前了。其它版本何时会加入这一功能目前还不得而知，不过 Mac 用户在今日内就可以更新了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/04/evernote-for-mac-now-lets-you-search-using-everyday-language/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://evernote.com/evernote/\" target=\"_blank\">Evernote (1)</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://evernote.com/contact/support/kb/#%21/article/38949727\" target=\"_blank\">(2)</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/04/evernote-for-mac-now-lets-you-search-using-everyday-language/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20822781/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/04/evernote-for-mac-now-lets-you-search-using-everyday-language/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
